      <scopecontent id="aspace_c6bca8d9b169b919c0c945b9530d4a74">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of student files and registration cards maintained by the School of Engineering for students in the classes of 1917-1970, including records for students who left prior to graduation.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_eec3201f3b0b8e09db639dfb57661344">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>Some records in this finding aid have been redacted, as they include student names, donor names, and other restricted data. These records will not appear in the published finding aid.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
